":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garment as it is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when complete:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in both of these senses it is used in the present day]: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiToEapN","text_ar":"قِطْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a garment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~ap","text_ar":"شُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viyaAb","text_ar":"ثِيَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus, and thus only, in the S, meaning of garments and of cloths, for it is of both,] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong piece;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabiybapN musotaTiylapN","text_ar":"سَبِيبَةٌ مُسْتَطِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [it is often applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong piece of cloth of those pieces of which a tent is composed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqaqN","text_ar":"شُقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iqaAqN","text_ar":"شِقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, Mgh, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yabiyEu $iqaAqa Alkat~aAni","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَبِيعُ شِقَاقَ الكَتَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one sells pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblong pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of linen"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (B, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bSr","text_ar":"بصر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of Hell; likewise pronounced ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 816.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A far journey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) sometimes thus pronounced with kesr: (S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a far, long journey: a far-extending space:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a road difficult to him who travels it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vnyA","text_ar":"ثنيا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in my copy of the Msb, app. a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mountain-road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqaqN","text_ar":"شُقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A part, region, quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Arafeh, Er-Rághib, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards which one draws near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Arafeh, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards which the traveller directs himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uk~apN","text_ar":"شُكَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the reaching of which one is overtaken by difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA;) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","t